<div class="container py-5">

    <!-- Intro with Quick Links callout -->
    <div class="row mb-5 g-4 align-items-start">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <p class="lead">ACM CAIS 2026 (the "Conference"), part of the <strong>ACM Conference on AI and Agentic Systems</strong>, is committed to protecting the privacy of its attendees, authors, and other individuals with whom it interacts. This Privacy Policy ("Policy") explains how we collect, use, and maintain the privacy of personal information in connection with the Conference website at <a href="{{ site.url }}">{{ site.url }}</a> (the "Website").</p>
            <p>This Conference is sponsored by the <a href="https://www.acm.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Association for Computing Machinery</a> (ACM). For conference registration, paper submissions, and membership-related data, <a href="https://www.acm.org/about-acm/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ACM's Privacy Policy</a> applies. This Policy covers personal information collected through this Website specifically.</p>
            <p><small class="text-muted">Last updated: February 2026</small></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="quick-links-callout">
                <h2 class="h6 fw-bold">Quick Links</h2>
                <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                    <li><a href="https://www.acm.org/about-acm/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ACM Privacy Policy</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.acm.org/code-of-ethics" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ACM Code of Ethics</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#cookies">Cookie Policy</a></li>
